"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"### Get Clob Pair\\n\\nFetches the order book pair identified by a given ID, allowing users to retrieve detailed information about a specific trading pair within a Central Limit Order Book (CLOB) system.\\n\\nThe response includes data structured within the `ClobPair` schema.\\n\\n#### Method Declaration\\n\\n:::code-group\\n\\n```python [Python]\\nasync def get_clob_pair(self, pair_id: int) -> clob_pair_type.ClobPair\\n```\\n\\n```typescript [TypeScript]\\nasync getClobPair(pairId: number): Promise<ClobModule.QueryClobPairResponse>\\n```\\n\\n```rust [Rust]\\npub async fn get_clob_pair(&mut self, pair_id: u32) -> Result<ClobPair, Error>\\n```\\n\\n```url [API]\\n/dydxprotocol.clob.Query/ClobPair\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\\n#### Parameters\\n\\n| Parameter | Location | Type  | Required | Description  |\\n| --------- | -------- | ----- | -------- | ------------ |\\n| `id`      | query    | [u32] | true     | Clob pair ID |\\n\\n#### Response\\n\\n| Status | Meaning       | Schema     | Description                           |\\n| ------ | ------------- | ---------- | ------------------------------------- |\\n| `200`  | [OK]          | [ClobPair] | The clob pair information.            |\\n| `400`  | [Bad Request] |            | The request was malformed or invalid. |\\n| `404`  | [Not Found]   |            | The clob pair was not found.          |\\n\\nExamples: [Python] | [Rust] | [API]\\n\\n[Python]: https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-py-v2/examples/validator_get_example.py#L86\\n[Rust]: https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-rs/client/examples/validator_get.rs#L71\\n[API]: https://test-dydx-rest.kingnodes.com/dydxprotocol/clob/clob_pair/1\\n[u32]: /types/u32\\n[OK]: /types/ok\\n[ClobPair]: /types/clob_pair\\n[Bad Request]: /types/bad-request\\n[Not Found]: /types/not-found\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/node-client/public/get_c